because you are talented and hardworking.

312
00:21:50,881 --> 00:21:52,246
It has nothing to do with me.

313
00:21:52,700 --> 00:21:55,239
Even without me, there will be others.

314
00:21:55,522 --> 00:21:58,304
No, that's not the same.
How can someone else be the same?

315
00:22:00,263 --> 00:22:04,109
The first match of C-U-B-A.
Congratulations.

316
00:22:07,526 --> 00:22:09,977
Then, you must come and see it.

317
00:22:12,608 --> 00:22:13,672
Cheng Erluo.

318
00:22:15,620 --> 00:22:19,819
