333
00:24:04,314 --> 00:24:05,600
Of course.

334
00:24:05,684 --> 00:24:07,527
Do you really think so?

335
00:24:08,488 --> 00:24:10,287
Okay, I'll work hard to lose weight.

336
00:24:10,371 --> 00:24:11,809
Okay, I'll supervise you.

337
00:24:11,893 --> 00:24:14,097
Pinky promise. Do not break your promise.

338
00:24:52,170 --> 00:24:53,176
