339
00:24:55,885 --> 00:24:56,979
Why are you here?

340
00:24:57,920 --> 00:24:59,713
I thought I was just dreaming.

341
00:24:59,962 --> 00:25:01,879
I didn't expect you to come.

342
00:25:02,505 --> 00:25:03,569
Lie down first.

343
00:25:11,838 --> 00:25:12,893
Does it hurt?

344
00:25:14,254 --> 00:25:15,523
Do you know?

345
00:25:17,095 --> 00:25:18,447
I really wanted to win today.

346
00:25:20,709 --> 00:25:23,786
Even if you're not there,
I want to win it for you.

347
00:25:25,252 --> 00:25:26,355
I want to tell you,

348
00:25:27,821 --> 00:25:29,149
the one you used to like,

349
00:25:31,540 --> 00:25:32,683
is worthy.

350
00:25:38,089 --> 00:25:40,595
But I didn't expect
to prove it to you this way.

351
00:25:43,553 --> 00:25:44,578
I deserve this.

352
00:25:47,212 --> 00:25:48,608
It's not your fault.

353
00:25:49,431 --> 00:25:52,068
You are already very good,
really, it's not your fault.

354
00:25:53,088 --> 00:25:54,194
But the me in the past,

355
00:25:55,686 --> 00:25:56,868
everything was wrong.

356
00:26:00,596 --> 00:26:01,846
I was too stupid.

357
00:26:03,345 --> 00:26:05,288
Never realized your importance to me.

358
00:26:08,917 --> 00:26:13,477
I always wanted you to know,
our ten years is real.

359
00:26:14,257 --> 00:26:16,718
The Chubby Cheng by your side is not fake.

360
00:26:17,582 --> 00:26:19,369
Our previous feeling are not fake.

361
00:26:26,299 --> 00:26:27,960
I want to dance with you again.

362
00:26:28,516 --> 00:26:29,893
Beauty and the Beast's dance.

363
00:26:30,725 --> 00:26:32,658
To eat with you at the doorway again,

364
00:26:33,474 --> 00:26:35,047
braised meat and ice-cream.

365
00:26:38,028 --> 00:26:41,104
I want to see your encouraging smile
at the basketball court.

366
00:26:44,506 --> 00:26:46,078
These wishes...

367
00:26:47,695 --> 00:26:49,186
can they still come true?

368
00:26:54,173 --> 00:26:57,146
Promise me, don't get hurt anymore, okay?

369
00:26:58,902 --> 00:26:59,995
Got it.

370
00:27:27,511 --> 00:27:29,335
Who left the fruit basket here?

371
00:27:31,856 --> 00:27:32,999
Sorry, wrong room.

372
00:27:33,124 --> 00:27:34,130
Sorry, sorry.

373
00:27:34,214 --> 00:27:35,224
Xia Rui.

374
00:27:37,689 --> 00:27:39,047
