382
00:28:07,545 --> 00:28:09,752
If you bully Shu again, you will get it.

383
00:28:10,929 --> 00:28:12,268
Not too hard.

384
00:28:14,877 --> 00:28:18,198
Really. Acting lovey dovey in front of me.

385
00:28:29,941 --> 00:28:34,849
Little Shu, I still want a piece of cake.

386
00:28:35,273 --> 00:28:37,070
Can you order it for me?

387
00:28:37,828 --> 00:28:39,019
Order it yourself.

388
00:28:39,396 --> 00:28:43,380
My leg is broken.

389
00:28:43,713 --> 00:28:47,072
Please help me, or can I eat this one?

390
00:28:50,608 --> 00:28:51,613
Feed me.

391
00:28:55,109 --> 00:28:56,886
Okay. Open your mouth.

392
00:28:56,970 --> 00:28:58,296
Open your mouth.

393
